cial-intelligence tools. Google=E2=80=99s parent company Alphabet reported =
third-quarter revenue of $77 billion Tuesday, up 11% from the same period l=
ast year. The results marked the third consecutive quarter of accelerating =
growth for the search giant following an economic slowdown that briefly cau=
